  "detailed_description": "In the game \"Little Droid\" you will find exciting levels with a variety of traps, obstacles and riddles. You will explore amazing locations including a secret bunker, deep dungeons and mysterious forests. Each level offers new challenges and secrets to uncover.<br><br><strong>Little Droid</strong> is a classic 2D pixel art side-scrolling (metroidvania) adventure where you have to find the source of a mysterious signal. More than 20 secret rooms, many enemies and bosses. The droid will have to be constantly charged to complete the entire game.<br><br>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500570/extras/9634e2f42d7788b7c64c691ecaab42ab.webp?t=1767270428\" width=492 height=50 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Little droid adventure</h2> </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500570/extras/2886cd7da57acd45df243d54a869404f.poster.avif?t=1767270428\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500570/extras/2886cd7da57acd45df243d54a869404f.webm?t=1767270428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500570/extras/2886cd7da57acd45df243d54a869404f.mp4?t=1767270428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dangerous place</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500570/extras/98ffb255f19bbb77196894425ba16b9c.poster.avif?t=1767270428\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2500570/extras/98ffb255f19bbb77196894425ba16b9c.webm?t=1767270428\" type=